WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.666 --> 00:00:03.200
Your Majesty, please forgive me and punish me.

2
00:00:03.266 --> 00:00:06.233
I indeed made a jest of this matter. Please, get up.

3
00:00:09.566 --> 00:00:11.633
I was just worried that the wretch might harm you.

4
00:00:11.800 --> 00:00:13.833
What if he grabbed the dagger and took you hostage?

5
00:00:14.333 --> 00:00:16.100
I’m not that foolish.

6
00:00:16.100 --> 00:00:17.500
Fortunately, you’re fine.

7
00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:19.800
Don’t do such foolish things in the future.

8
00:00:19.800 --> 00:00:23.633
Otherwise, I would have to live a widow’s life, and you’d worry about me.

9
00:00:23.966 --> 00:00:26.133
In the future, I will be self-disciplined and cautious.

10
00:00:26.133 --> 00:00:27.200
Be careful.

11
00:00:30.466 --> 00:00:32.833
Ah, it’s me, Ruo Li.

12
00:00:35.066 --> 00:00:36.500
I still have medicines to deal with.

13
00:00:36.533 --> 00:00:38.100
Eat a little more.

14
00:00:39.066 --> 00:00:40.633
I’ll accompany you for a while.

15
00:00:42.700 --> 00:00:43.500
Ah.

16
00:00:46.200 --> 00:00:48.033
I’ll come back earlier tonight to keep you company.

17
00:00:49.966 --> 00:00:52.500
Ah, it seems like I’m getting more entangled with you.

18
00:01:04.866 --> 00:01:06.400
Gong Fei has been sent to the cold palace.

19
00:01:06.400 --> 00:01:07.833
There’s no chance of a comeback.

20
00:01:08.366 --> 00:01:11.233
I’ve fulfilled my agreement with the Empress Dowager.

21
00:01:11.800 --> 00:01:13.366
Are we leaving the palace?

22
00:01:16.333 --> 00:01:18.066
Ah, I’m really losing my mind.

23
00:01:18.266 --> 00:01:20.100
What’s more important than love? Freedom?

24
00:01:21.666 --> 00:01:22.466
Yuan.

25
00:01:23.066 --> 00:01:24.366
Go to Cining Palace.
